      Press release
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Fishermen urged to remove gear from non-UK waters ahead of Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">With two weeks until Brexit, fishermen who have deployed static gear in non-UK waters are being urged to get ready by removing it ahead of 31 October.</p>

  </div>
</div>

